text: Mohammad Aamer (born 8 August 1995) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 8 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Zarai Taraqiati Bank Limited cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
